name: AcuteRenalFailureUnspecifiedCauseICD10CM
title: Acute Renal Failure [Unspecified Cause] (ICD10CM)
purpose:
(Clinical Focus: This set of values contains diagnoses or problems that represent that the patient has  non-specific acute renal failure regardless of the clinical presentation of the condition),(Data Element Scope: Diagnoses or problems documented in a clinical record.),(Inclusion Criteria: N17	Acute kidney failure
N17.0	Acute kidney failure with tubular necrosis
N17.1	Acute kidney failure with acute cortical necrosis
N17.2	Acute kidney failure with medullary necrosis
N17.9	Acute kidney failure, unspecified
N17.8	Other acute kidney failure),(Exclusion Criteria: None)
